# NOTE on .meta files:
#   ALL .meta files under Assets/ and Packages/ MUST be committed (including
#   for Asset Store imports). Unity uses meta GUIDs to resolve every reference
#   in scenes/prefabs — losing them = silently broken refs after re-import.
#   v1's selective allowlist approach caused exactly this issue with the Kit.
